summary: AN ORDINANCE amending Section 1 of Ordinance 110997 to correct a typographical error in the statement of the total sum of the approved and confirmed assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 6718 for the improvement of Rainier Avenue South, east side only, from 39th Avenue South to approximately 120 feet north of South Edmunds Street, under Ordinance 108720, as amended.
